item.title: CVE-2020-4722|2024-09-16T16:28:10.389Z -- ibm -- i2%20analyst%20notebook
item.description: IBM i2 Analyst Notebook 9.2.0 and 9.2.1 could allow a local attacker to execute arbitrary code on the system, caused by a memory corruption. By persuading a victim to open a specially-crafted file, an attacker could exploit this vulnerability to execute arbitrary code on the system. IBM X-Force ID: 187870.
